OL,4,Ccompensation schemes as 'Quasi-
OL,5,CKangaroo Courts'
OL,7,FSir Alan Bates has criticised the
OL,8,FGovernment's handling of compensation
OL,9,Ffor victims of the Horizon IT scandal,
OL,10,Fdescribing the process as resembling
OL,11,F"quasi-kangaroo courts."
OL,13,FThe former subpostmaster and justice
OL,14,Fcampaigner said he was recently
OL,15,Foffered a compensation amount that he
OL,16,Fclaims is less than half of what he
OL,17,Finitially requested.
