OL,7,FWriting in the Sunday Times, the 70-
OL,8,Fyear-old said: "The sub-postmaster
OL,9,Fcompensation schemes have been turned
OL,10,Fin
OL,12,Fto quasi-kangaroo courts in which the
OL,13,FDepartment for Business and Trade sits
OL,14,Fin judgement of the claims and alters
OL,15,Fthe goal posts as and when it chooses.
OL,17,F"Claims are, and have been, knocked
OL,18,Fback on the basis that legally you
OL,19,Fwould not be able to make them, or
OL,20,Fthat the parameters of the scheme do
OL,21,Fnot extend to certain items."
