OL,7,FA specific scheme`the Group Litigation
OL,8,FOrder (GLO)`was created for the 555
OL,9,Fclaimants who had sued the Post Office
OL,10,Fin the High Court from 2017 to 2019.
OL,12,FUnder this scheme, claimants can
OL,13,Feither accept a fixed #75,000 payment
OL,14,For negotiate a bespoke settlement.
OL,15,FDisputed claims are reviewed by an
OL,16,Findependent panel, with a final appeal
OL,17,Foption to former High Court judge Sir
OL,18,FRoss Cranston.
