OL,4,Ccompensation schemes as 'Quasi-
OL,5,CKangaroo Courts'
OL,7,FSir Alan, whose story featured in
OL,8,FITV's Mr Bates vs The Post Office,
OL,9,Fsaid earlier promises that the
OL,10,Fcompensation process would be "non-
OL,11,Flegalistic" have proven "worthless."
OL,13,FHe is now calling for an independent
OL,14,Fbody to oversee compensation not only
OL,15,Ffor this case but for future public
OL,16,Fsector scandals.
OL,18,FKnighted last year for his justice
OL,19,Fefforts, Sir Alan founded the Justice
OL,20,Ffor Subpostmasters Alliance (JFSA).
