OL,7,FIt's believed that around 80% of
OL,8,Fclaimants in Sir Alan's group have
OL,9,Feither accepted their full settlement
OL,10,For received the majority of it.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,13,FBusiness and Trade responded: "We
OL,14,Fdeeply respect all those affected by
OL,15,Fthis scandal, including Sir Alan, for
OL,16,Fhis determined advocacy.
