OL,7,FSince taking office, we've quadrupled
OL,8,Ftotal payouts to postmasters. We
OL,9,Funderstand that evidence may be
OL,10,Flimited due to the passage of time, so
OL,11,Fwe strive to give postmasters the
OL,12,Fbenefit of the doubt.
OL,14,FThose dissatisfied with their offer
OL,15,Fcan request an independent panel
OL,16,Freview, entirely separate from
OL,17,Fgovernment influence."
